    "401225": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It was okay. His attitude could use some work, though."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "I see. In that case, I regret to announce that Deakin here has just missed the best opportunity in his prison career to be promoted."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Deakin",
                    "T": "I... uh, I admit that I was only thinking about the coupons... I'm sorry to have disappointed you, Your Grace. I originally... I once hoped for a chance to do some higher-level work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Deakin",
                    "T": "*sigh* I had no idea you two were big shots who were worthy of speaking with His Grace... Losing out on such a big opportunity because I couldn't see past my own nose..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Plenty of time ahead, Deakin. There will be more opportunities."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Well, I believe that concludes the introductions. We've already taken enough time here. Deakin, if you would."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Deakin",
                    "T": "Yes! Your Grace, I'll take my leave now!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Please, follow me. To make you feel more welcome, I'll show you around the various facilities of the Fortress of Meropide. I hope it will help you adjust to life here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "He's going to personally give us a tour? Paimon can't figure out what this guy's thinking at all..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's just roll with it for now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But I hope he doesn't know too much already."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "No wonder Charlotte's so interested in him! He's one of those mysterious types. Alright, let's keep up with him."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
