    "401549": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#*stretching* Are you awake, {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm? What's wrong? You seem to have something on your mind... Did you dream about something last night?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I dreamed of Childe..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Rather, in the dream, I was Childe..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is that even possible? Unless... It wasn't an ordinary dream?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ah.... Childe's Vision! So you had it with you this whole time..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Maybe the Vision connected Childe's consciousness to yours?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Maybe I can use his Vision..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "To see everything he experienced from his perspective."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And our investigation has its first major breakthrough! Good thing you brought the Vision with you here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So what did you see in the dream? Do you know where Childe went?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The dream was a little hazy..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And I didn't see anything particularly useful."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh, okay... Well, hopefully it'll be a bit more helpful in the future."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's more important now is that it's the start of another new day as prisoners. Let's do our best to earn more Credit Coupons!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's the plan for today?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's go work in the production zone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's spend some coupons to skip work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? You want to spend our coupons on slacking off already? We'd better go to work and earn some more coupons first. We'll have more room to relax once we've got some spare coupons to fall back on!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's go, it's time to start working. If that guard Fielding catches us skulking about, he's sure to give us an earful."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "401567": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Fielding",
                    "T": "Hey, Traveler, Paimon! Package here for ya."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fielding",
                    "T": "The next time you buy something, go pick it up yourself. I'm not a deliveryman, you know."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Huh? A package... For us? Did you buy something, {NICKNAME}? *yawn* Paimon's not quite awake yet, so why don't you go take a look..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I didn't buy anything."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Unless, this is..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ah, right! Yesterday we broke the \"hidden rule\" and bought tickets for both boxers. Maybe this package is the \"bad thing\" that Collins said would happen..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, Paimon suddenly feels wide awake! Wait, maybe let Paimon go hide somewhere first. Just call for Paimon AFTER you've opened it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, wait, wait! Paimon's still here, don't open it! Ahh!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Doesn't seem especially scary."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But there is something a little odd inside."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? What is it? Are you okay?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "L—Let Paimon take a peek too..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, it's just a small bottle... but the color of the liquid inside looks so wrong, almost like..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Hmm, rumor has it that a boxer went missing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And the liquid in the bottle obviously looks like blood..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright, that's enough of that! No need to say it out loud, Paimon already knows what you're trying to say..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Do you want to give it a sniff?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Do you want to give it a taste?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Blegh, no way! Get that stuff away from Paimon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Seems we'll have to investigate."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "This place is chock-full of strange happenings after all..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon thinks we shouldn't open the bottle until we've figured out what's going on. Just trust Paimon on this one, okay!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What do you plan on doing now?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
