    "401580": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "#Oh? You must be {NICKNAME}, huh? Sorry, mate, but competitors as strong as you are prohibited from participating. I don't make the rules, mind you, but I was given very specific instructions..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "Even convicts value their lives, don't they? I hope you can understand, haha..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "But we have a game here that'll let you show off your strength, and you'll even earn some Credit Coupons in the process. What do you think? Interested?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And if we lose the game? Will it cost us Credit Coupons?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "Of course! That's the cruel reality facing every competitor in a place like the Pankration Ring."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Alright, I'll give it a try."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "OK. Great, let me walk you through the rules."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "The targets in front of you will pop up one after another."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "You'll need to hit the targets in the same order that they popped up. If you can complete a few rounds in a row with no mistakes, then you'll win Credit Coupons."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "But the second you mess up the order, you lose. Game over."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "The game costs 300 Credit Coupons to have a go. So, you up for it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I don't have enough coupons..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "Then come back once you've got enough coupons, I'll still be here to start the game for ya."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
