    "401561": {
        "Desc": "Walk around and look for clues",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "I heard you crazy fools really did it, you bought tickets to support both fighters, didn't ya? Well? Did anything happen?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, the next day we received a mysterious package, but we still haven't made any sense of the contents..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "So it is real... You didn't become cursed or anything like that, did ya? Are you both still okay? Wait, are you sure that it's still you controlling your bodies right now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Uh, Paimon's not sure... What do you think, {NICKNAME}? Is Paimon still Paimon?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Only you'd ever ask such a question, so I'm pretty sure you're fine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, okay... well, that's good!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "Yeah, you two don't seem to have changed at all, but I wouldn't let your guard down just yet..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "Still, I didn't expect you would actually do it. You'd actually throw away coupons like that, just to satisfy your curiosity?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Even if we bought tickets like everybody else, it's not like we could hope to earn any coupons..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "When it comes to things like this, it's always the organizer who makes the real profits."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "Hey, just what are you trying to imply? The Pankration Ring is an honest business, and we really don't make much from selling tickets..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "We make so little that even the current tournaments can only be held thanks to funding from the producer of Fonta."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, so it's the company that manufactures Fonta sponsoring the events? Paimon thought all of this was thanks to the Duke's support."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "Let's just say it's a mutually beneficial arrangement... They reached out to us first, hoping to promote Fonta products in the Fortress of Meropide."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I understand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That's some important info."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collins",
                    "T": "*sigh* Anyway, you try and take extra good care of yourselves these next few days, you hear?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
