    "401551": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon's beat... but after so many shifts, it seems we're really getting the hang of it now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It does seem to be getting easier."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "All you do is float around telling me what to do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "Hey there, fellow shift-mates! I saw you just finished your work so I thought I'd come over and say hi."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, hey there! We've seen you before, your assigned workspace is really close, isn't it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "Haha, that's right. The name's Rowan. These past few days I couldn't help but notice the new faces working nearby, I guess we were destined to meet."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "I've been working here for almost 15 years. Even the foreman, Grainville, always calls me \"Chief.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa, you've been working here a long time, Chief!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Hey, Chief."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "In other words, you haven't managed any improvement in 15 years."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey! Not so loud..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "Hahaha... If there's anything you'd like to know, just ask me. I know the work here in the production zone better than the back of my hand."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright, Chief! We'll be sure to come to you first!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I think I've got the work more or less down pat..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We just haven't quite learned all the \"rules.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "Did you just ask about... the \"rules\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "Heh, pretty sharp for newcomers. You've already heard about the \"rules,\" huh? ...Who'd you hear it from?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I don't think you need to know that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The \"hidden rules\"... That's what they're called, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "Hmm... Alright, seeing as I'm the one who came over here and you're already callin' me \"Chief,\" I guess I can tell you a little."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "Truth is, you two keep workin' like this, you might be puttin' yourselves in danger."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Wait, there's even a rule about that? What would've happened if you never told us about this...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "Well, it's usually not that easy to break one on accident... The conditions of the \"hidden rules\" are usually pretty specific, but once you do break one, bad things happen."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So the conditions in this case are...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "If you work continuously in the production zone for three days, and if all you do besides eating and sleeping is just work..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "Then something bad will happen during lunch on the third day."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh! Like what!? Oooh, don't scare Paimon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "Heh, if I knew that, then I wouldn't be standing here talking to you, now would I?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You mean, even you have never tried working three days like that before?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "There's actually a legend about this rule..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "They say that there was a worker who worked way harder than me. He was both efficient and eager on the job, and most other workers couldn't hold a candle to him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "One time, he tried to test his limits and worked as long as he could. Then, during lunch on the third day..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "He disappeared into thin air, as if he'd evaporated. Later, some people went and asked some of his past friends about him, but they said... \"Never heard of the guy.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What the...!? How could that happen?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What did that worker look like?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Did you ever see him?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "Unfortunately, we were assigned different production zones. I never saw for myself what he looked like."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait, are you thinking that it was..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Thank you very much for the information."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We'll give it a try..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "Oh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rowan",
                    "T": "You... *sigh* Listen, kid, this ain't the kind of thing you should be curious about. Let me tell you, you're better off forgetting about it and looking after yourself. Now I kinda regret ever telling you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, I agree with Chief here... Do you really want to try?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It sounds like a good lead to me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Nothing ventured, nothing gained."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, alright... If you insist..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
