    "401562": {
        "Desc": "Walk around and look for clues",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, what are these papers scattered all over the ground? Are they registration forms or something?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm, maybe not... Every page has the Fonta Co. symbol on it. Maybe it's some flyers from the company?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's take a look before anyone else shows up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, okay. But if someone catches us, they could accuse us of trying to steal the company's secrets, couldn't they?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What're you afraid of? We're already convicted criminals."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, hehe, you're right! Guess there's nothing to worry about then, let Paimon have a look here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Without assistance from the Fontaine Research Institute, development of the new product has been slow, and some researchers on the project have voiced concerns."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We have no choice but to let the new product undergo the first phase of promotional trials without a designated name or packaging. We will adjust the direction of future development according to feedback..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We have decided to only conduct closed, small-scale trials for the time being..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sure doesn't seem like anything unusual... The company is just trying to develop some new products besides Fonta, but it sounds like things aren't going well at all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's put these papers back where we found them, and make it look like nobody went through them... Okay, good."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "401563": {
        "Desc": "Walk around and look for clues",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Promoter",
                    "T": "*sigh* If there's no way to send it all out, then maybe I'll never get a chance to leave..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, who are you? We've never seen you before, and you don't look like a fellow convict."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Promoter",
                    "T": "I'm not! Of course I'm not. Please don't mistake me for a criminal, I'm a good, law-abiding citizen."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Then what are you doing here? You sure seem anxious about something."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Promoter",
                    "T": "I'm a promoter for Fonta Co., and I'm usually responsible for promoting our drink products. I thought I could complete my task here quickly and return to headquarters, but I've been here way longer than I anticipated..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, a promoter from Fonta Co.! So what kind of problem did you run into?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Promoter",
                    "T": "Ugh, I'm so upset... It's all because of that Duke."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Promoter",
                    "T": "After discussing the company's promotional plans with him, he told me outright that my project was worthless."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Promoter",
                    "T": "However, in light of our long history of successful collaboration, I still tried to patiently explain the details. However, to my surprise, he just cut me off while I was speaking!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Promoter",
                    "T": "Let me take a moment and recall his exact words..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Promoter",
                    "T": "I'm just gonna stop you there and say no. If anything, I'm saving you time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Promoter",
                    "T": "It seems you don't fully understand the value of Credit Coupons here, nor do you understand the value of your own products. The former is because you are from the overworld, that's understandable and I don't blame you for that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Promoter",
                    "T": "But as for the latter, only someone monumentally stupid, so breathtakingly stupid that they were completely ignorant of the value of Credit Coupons despite living in the underworld would ever possibly consider buying your drink. Let's just forget it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Promoter",
                    "T": "Anyway, that's how he rejected my proposal and asked me to come up with another solution with the condition that it doesn't cause any trouble for him. Can you believe that guy...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, well, he is the head honcho here. Not much you can do about that. We met him too and could tell that he's the kind of guy that's hard to pin down."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Promoter",
                    "T": "Fine, fine, I should just let it go... I'm on his turf, after all. His house, his rules."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
