    "401813": {
        "Desc": "Ask the trio that hangs out together often",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Vidoc",
                    "T": "Oho, seeing you at this time must mean you've already saved up a lot of Credit Coupons. Or at least enough to skip work... Heh, seems you're getting into the swing of things around here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We're getting by."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "My goal is to become the next Duke!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vidoc",
                    "T": "Impressive... Very impressive..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, now can you tell us about the hidden rules you know?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vidoc",
                    "T": "Ah, if that's what you what to know, I guess you couldn't have come at a better time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh, what do you mean it's a good time?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vidoc",
                    "T": "Leonide and those other pesky broke urchins have all gone to work in the production zone. I wouldn't want them listening in without paying up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We get it, just tell us already!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vidoc",
                    "T": "So, you know those pipes that make strange sounds? Don't ever, ever go near them at night. Even if you manage to avoid the guards, you might find something even more terrible there..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Something even more terrible? Like what?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vidoc",
                    "T": "A group of cannibals."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Cannibals!? In the Fortress of Meropide!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vidoc",
                    "T": "Every month, they meet a few times in the dead of night. Rumor has it that they might be connected to the people that've disappeared here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vidoc",
                    "T": "But what's even scarier is that they have a \"special\" proclivity..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vidoc",
                    "T": "Since they have no way to dispose of the leftover remains, they have ways to transform them into other forms and keep them in the Fortress forever."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, Paimon might already know what you mean by \"other forms\"... So that's what's going on here. Ugh, Paimon's stomach doesn't feel so good..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Is that really true?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "There's still a chance that what we saw isn't connected to cannibals."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vidoc",
                    "T": "Hehe, you two look pretty skeptical. No matter, learning the truth behind dark secrets isn't necessarily a good thing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vidoc",
                    "T": "I've got things to do too. I suggest you just act like I never told you anything."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, can we just trust him on this one? Oh, Paimon doesn't want her blood and flesh entombed here for all eternity..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Even if it's true..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Do you really think cannibals could take me in a fight?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh... So that's how you see the situation... Huh. Y'know, Paimon does feel a little better about it now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Alright, then just like before..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's get ready to investigate another hidden rule."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "*sigh* When will all the secrets end?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Brimming with curiosity, you and Paimon eat lunch and head out to investigate this new \"hidden rule\"..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
